ee/2011/aug/07/tottenham-riot-broadwater-farm| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

现实因素包括当地是个多族裔混居区——它聚集了大量的非洲－加勒比、西非、库尔德、土耳其裔塞浦路斯、土耳其、爱尔兰和葡萄牙后裔的移民；近三十年来，区内各族关系紧张，而非洲－加勒比裔同当地警察之间更是长期处于紧张状态。该地具有比较高的贫穷与失业率，作为伦敦的一个贫困区，当地的失业率比全国平均水平高出近两倍，人均寿命比伦敦平均水平低5岁，各类犯罪较为多发。富人与穷人之间的隔阂，很低的[[社会流动|社会流动]]，以及民众对政府为了减少债务而削减公共开支的不满<ref name="NinaP">{{cite news|last=Power|first=Nina|title=There is a context to London's riots that cannot be ignored|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2011/aug/08/context-london-riots|date=2011-08-08|newspaper=Guardian|accessdate=2011-08-10|archive-date=2011-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110810052320/http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2011/aug/08/context-london-riots|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Deaths in police custody since 1998: 333; officers convicted: none|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2010/dec/03/deaths-police-custody-officers-convicted|date=2010-12-03|newspaper=Guardian|accessdate=2011-08-10|archive-date=2011-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110827093014/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2010/dec/03/deaths-police-custody-officers-convicted|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#1">{{cite news|title=OECD: UK has worse social mobility record than other developed countries|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2010/mar/10/oecd-uk-worst-social-mobility|date=2010-03-10|newspaper=Guardian|accessdate=2011-08-10|archive-date=2011-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110827110005/http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2010/mar/10/oecd-uk-worst-social-mobility|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 射杀马克·达根 ===
[[File:Ferry_Lane,_Tottenham_Hale_-_geograph.org.uk_-_1767129.jpg|thumb]]
枪杀事件发生于8月4日晚上，当时警察正准备对乘坐在一辆[[計程車|計程車]]车里的[[马克·達根|马克·達根]]实施逮捕，地点位于托特纳姆地铁站附近的一座桥上——Ferry Lane bridge<ref name=bbc2nd /><ref name=camber>{{Cite news| last = Camber| first = Rebecca| title = Mark Duggan shot by police in back of London cab after an alleged shootout| work = Daily Mail| location = UK| accessdate = 2011-08-07| date = 2011-08-07| url = http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2022670/Gangster-Mark-Duggan-shot-police-London-cab-shootout.html| archive-date = 2011-08-10| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110810042435/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2022670/Gangster-Mark-Duggan-shot-police-London-cab-shootout.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

该事件目前由{{tsl|en|Independent Police Complaints Commission|独立警察投诉委员会}}调查处理<ref name=bbc2nd>{{cite news  |title=Man dead and police officer hurt in Tottenham shooting  |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14412752  |newspaper=BBC News  |date=2011-08-05  |accessdate=2011-08-06  |archive-date=2011-08-09  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110809025354/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14412752  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>。该委员会负责处理民众死于警察的事件。目前还不完全确定警察当时为何要逮捕马克·達根，IPCC表示逮捕行动是{{tsl|en|Operation Trident (Metropolitan Police)|打击枪支犯罪行动}}的一部分，而马克·達根是警方怀疑的一个与[[可卡因|可卡因]]交易有关的持枪的罪犯<ref name="guardian-06-duggan">{{cite news|title=Tottenham in flames as protesters riot|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/aug/06/police-cars-attacked-tottenham-mark-duggan|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2011-08-06|archive-date=2011-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110808053935/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/aug/06/police-cars-attacked-tottenham-mark-duggan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

