=== 示威活动 ===
8月6日举行了一场和平示威活动，起点始于{{link-en|Broadwater农场|Broadwater Farm}}终止于托特纳姆警察局<ref name="bolesworth">{{Cite news| last = Bolesworth| first = Sarah| coauthors = Barry Neild, Peter Beaumont, Paul Lewis, Sandra Laville| title = Tottenham in flames as riot follows protest| work = The Observer| location = London| accessdate = 2011-08-07| date = 2011-08-07| url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/aug/06/tottenham-riots-protesters-police| archive-date = 2013-07-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130705124332/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/aug/06/tottenham-riots-protesters-police| dead-url = no}}</ref>。这起示威是由死者的亲人和朋友发起的，其中包括当地居民和社区负责人，目的是要求获得真相和公正<ref name="guardian-06-duggan" /><ref name="autogenerated1">{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14423942 |title=Tottenham police shooting: Dead man was minicab passenger |work=BBC News |date=2011-08-05 |accessdate=2011-08-07 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123182319/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14423942 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.channel4.com/news/police-patrol-tottenham-after-riots |title=Tottenham riots are a disgrace, says MP |publisher=Channel4.com |accessdate=2011-08-07 |archive-date=2011-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110901045616/http://www.channel4.com/news/police-patrol-tottenham-after-riots |dead-url=no }}</ref>，大约有200人参加<ref name="Guardian-07-peaceful" />。后来，一名警官同示威群众谈话，不过他们要求同更高职位的长官来跟他们谈。由于对警方的答复不满意，所以他们站在警局前面的几个小时比他们原计划的时间要长。根据目击者称，在傍晚有一个更年轻且更激动的人群也来到了那里，其中一些人手里拿着武器。当他们听说警察攻击了一名16岁的女孩时暴力活动就开始了<ref name="jackson" /><ref name="Guardian-07-peaceful" />。大约20:20（当地时间），其中的一些人开始攻击附近的两辆[[警车|警车]]并将之点燃。之后骚乱在该地开始蔓延，随后波及到伦敦其他地区，乃至伦敦以外的其他英格兰城市<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/breaking/2011/0809/breaking25.html|title=Timeline - British disorder by dates|date=2011-08-09|work=irishtimes.com|accessdate=2011-08-10|archive-date=2012-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024145918/http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/breaking/2011/0809/breaking25.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/aug/07/tottenham-riots-peaceful-protest|title=Tottenham riots: a peaceful protest, then suddenly all hell broke loose|last=Lewis|first=Paul|date=2011-08-07|work=guardian.co.uk|accessdate=2011-08-10|archive-date=2013-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130218094330/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/aug/07/tottenham-riots-peaceful-protest|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 原因 ==
综合各种媒体的报道，该地发生骚乱主要有以下多种原因：

* 警察造成有疑點的致命射击事件
* 当地民众与警察之间的紧张关系<ref name="jackson" />
* 高失业率，尤其是年轻人失业率更高<ref name="Reuters"/><ref name="Croft"/><ref name="msnbc.msn.com"/><ref name="dlammy"/><ref name="Somaiya"/>：据报道，英国16-24岁的年轻人中约有18%是失业者，黑人青年的失业比例更高达一半以上<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/lundunsaoluan/content-3/detail_2011_08/12/8345730_0.shtml |language= |title=大逮捕近1200人 英全国骚乱渐息 |publisher=新京报 |date=2011年8月12日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2019年9月5日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905064252/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/lundunsaoluan/content-3/detail_2011_08/12/8345730_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*政府削减公共开支；青年俱乐部和社区项目等“软服务”的开支削减严重。
* [[黑帮|黑帮]]文化<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/lundunsaoluan/content-3/detail_2011_08/11/8336014_0.shtml |language= |title=英民调显示民众将骚乱归咎黑帮 不怪罪政府紧缩 |publisher=中国新闻网 |date=2011年8月11日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2019年9月10日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190910182452/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/lundunsaoluan/content-3/detail_2011_08/11/8336014_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* [[经济危机|经济危机]]的波及<ref>{{Cite news| last = Riddell| first = Mary| title = London riots: the underclass lashes out| work = The Telegraph| location = London| date = 2011-08-08| accessdate = 2011-08-09| url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/law-and-order/8630533/Riots-the-underclass-lashes-out.html| archive-date = 2020-12-10| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201210052126/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/law-and-order/8630533/Riots-the-underclass-lashes-out.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>
* 较多的贫穷人口以及明显的贫富差距<ref name="NinaP"/><ref>{{Cite news| last = Topping| first = Alexandra| title = Looting 'fuelled by social exclusion'| work = The Guardian| location = London| date = 2011-08-08| accessdate = 2011-08-09| url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/aug/08/looting-fuelled-by-social-exclusion| archive-date = 2013-03-10| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130310075841/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/aug/08/looting-fuelled-by-social-exclusion| dead-url = no}}</ref>
* [[已開發國家|已開發國家]]中[[社会流动|社会流动]]不足<ref name="#1"/>
* [[投机主义|机会主义者]]犯罪分子<ref name="Rioting spirals out of control"/>
* 娱乐消遣性的暴力<ref name="tvnz.co.nz"/>
* 据报道，[[英格兰|英格兰]]西内陆的警察对寻衅[[暴動|暴動]]者表现软弱，存在纵容行为<ref name="greed">{{cite news |title=How rioting spread around England |work=BBC News |date=2011-08-09 |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-14466477 |accessdate=2011-08-09 |archive-date=2016-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202122828/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-14466477 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

