=== 政界 ===
正在意大利休假的[[英国首相|英国首相]][[戴维·卡梅伦|戴维·卡梅伦]]，此前声称不会提前结束假期，但鉴于事态严重，他于8日晚间提前返回伦敦，并将于9日主持召开针对暴乱的高级安全会议。政府一位发言人称，卡梅伦度假期间时刻关注着事态的发展。此前声称对警方“信心十足”且不准备缩短假期的伦敦市长[[鲍里斯·约翰逊|鲍里斯·约翰逊]]，已确定提前结束假期，于9日返回伦敦处理骚乱事件。8日上午也提前结束休假返回伦敦的内政大臣[[特雷莎·梅|特雷莎·梅]]，当天会见了伦敦警察局代理专员蒂姆·戈德温。她谴责近日发生的骚乱行为是“绝对的犯罪行为”，并要求这些人接受制裁。副首相尼克·克莱格8日下午前往托特纳姆地区检视受损状况，他称暴乱会给当地社区留下“巨大的伤疤”，他强调政府应该全方位参与社区的重建。

代表托特纳姆地区来自[[工党_(英国)|工党]]的[[英国国会|英国国会]]议员[[大衛·拉米|大衛·拉米]]（David Lammy）在该地发生骚乱后，他呼吁平静下来，说“随着调查的进行真相和公正肯定会出来”<ref>{{cite news|title=David Lammy Appeals for Calm after Tottenham Riots|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2011/08/07/david-lammy-appeals-for-c_n_920360.html|work=Huffington Post|location=USA|accessdate=2011-08-07|date=2011-08-07|archive-date=2012-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112100207/http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2011/08/07/david-lammy-appeals-for-c_n_920360.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他也说骚乱者并不代表整个托特纳姆地区的居民<ref name="guardian1">{{cite web |first=Andrew |last=Sparrow |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/politics/2011/aug/07/politicians-condemn-tottenham-riots |title=Politicians condemn Tottenham riots |work=The Guardian |date=2011-08-07 |accessdate=2011-08-07 |archive-date=2013-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130402172118/http://www.guardian.co.uk/politics/2011/aug/07/politicians-condemn-tottenham-riots |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他坚持要求IPCC必须彻查出马克的死因<ref name=lammy />。代表[[斯特里漢姆_(英國國會選區)|斯特里漢姆]]地区的国会议员[[丘卡·烏馬納|丘卡·烏馬納]]（Chuka Umunna）谴责发生在布里克斯顿和托特纳姆的暴力事件<ref name="guardian3">{{cite web |author=Sam Jones, Paul Lewis, Matthew Taylor and Ben Quinn |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/aug/08/london-riots-spread-second-night |title=London riots spread south of Thames |work=The Guardian |location=UK |date=2011-07-08 |accessdate=2011-08-08 |archive-date=2013-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602071452/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/aug/08/london-riots-spread-second-night |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="yourlocalguardian1">{{cite web |url=http://www.yourlocalguardian.co.uk/news/local/streathamnews/9183106.UPDATE__Looters_cause_chaos_in_Streatham_and_Brixton/ |title=Looters cause chaos in Streatham and Brixton |publisher=Yourlocalguardian.co.uk |accessdate=2011-08-08 |archive-date=2018-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116054040/https://www.yourlocalguardian.co.uk/news/local/streathamnews/9183106.UPDATE__Looters_cause_chaos_in_Streatham_and_Brixton/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="streathamguardian1">{{cite web |url=http://www.streathamguardian.co.uk/news/9183409.UPDATE__Lambeth_Council_leader__They_were_looters_not_rioters_/ |title=UPDATE: Lambeth Council leader "They were looters not rioters". (From Streatham Guardian) |publisher=Streathamguardian.co.uk |accessdate=2011-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110930030826/http://www.streathamguardian.co.uk/news/9183409.UPDATE__Lambeth_Council_leader__They_were_looters_not_rioters_/ |archive-date=2011-09-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

