[[英国首相办公室|英国首相办公室]]发言人表示：“昨晚托特纳姆发生的骚乱绝对令人难以接受，那些攻击警察和民众、破坏财产的行为没有正当理由”<ref name=patrol-streets>{{cite news|title=London riots: Police patrol streets after violence|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14435251|work=BBC News|date=2011-08-07|accessdate=2011-08-07|archive-date=2011-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110809203535/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14435251|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

