英国首相卡梅伦谴责道“掠夺者，破坏财物的人，窃贼，抢劫犯所做的是令人厌恶的事情”，他告戒骚乱者“你们将知道法律的威严，如果你的年龄让你实施了这些犯罪，那么你们也足够面临惩罚”<ref name="BBC news">{{cite web | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14460554 | title=UK riots: Trouble erupts in English cities | accessdate=2011-08-10 | archive-date=2020-12-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208032104/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14460554 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。代表[[中克羅伊登_(英國國會選區)|中克羅伊登]]的[[国会议员|国会议员]][[加文·巴維爾|加文·巴維爾]]（Gavin Barwell），也称一些地区遭受的破坏是“令人厌恶的”<ref>{{cite web|last=Your Local Guardian|title=Riot Fall Out Hits Croydon|url=http://www.yourlocalguardian.co.uk/news/local/topstories/9183466.LIVE__Riot_fallout_hits_Croydon/|accessdate=2011-08-08|archive-date=2011-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111124051224/http://www.yourlocalguardian.co.uk/news/local/topstories/9183466.LIVE__Riot_fallout_hits_Croydon/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

