在伯明翰的一个寺庙受到袭击后，'''Sangat TV''' 和 '''Sikh Channel'''这两家电视台呼吁他们的观众去保护'''Gurudwara'''地区的[[锡克教|锡克教]]的庙宇——'''Sikh temples'''以免遭暴力破坏<ref>{{cite news|url=http://media247.co.uk/bizasia/newsarchive/2011/08/sangat_tv_switc.php|work=BizAsia|date=2011-08-09|title=Sangat TV switches to Birmingham riots coverage|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120408214116/http://media247.co.uk/bizasia/newsarchive/2011/08/sangat_tv_switc.php|archivedate=2012-04-08|accessdate=2011-08-12}}</ref>。9日和10日夜晚，Sikh社区的志愿者（大多数是[[锡克族|锡克族]]）走到Gurudwara各地站岗放哨，他们由200到300名不同年龄的人组成<ref>{{cite web |last=Singh |first=Tejashdeep |url=http://www.sikhsiyasat.net/2011/08/10/sikhs-stood-guard-to-protect-gurudwaras-from-rioters-in-southall/ |title=Sikhs stood guard to protect Gurudwaras from rioters in Southall |publisher=Sikhsiyasat.net |date=2011-07-23 |accessdate=2011-08-11 |archive-date=2020-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814144943/https://sikhsiyasat.net/2011/08/10/sikhs-stood-guard-to-protect-gurudwaras-from-rioters-in-southall/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-14470772 |title=Southall Sikhs stand against London rioters |publisher=Bbc.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2011-08-11 |archive-date=2017-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170417201244/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-14470772 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

10日，在'''Eltham'''，大约有200名来自一个[[极右翼|极右翼]]的民间组织——{{tsl|en|English Defence League|保卫英国同盟}}的成员支持警察与一个扔瓶子的暴乱人群对抗。该组织东南地区的负责人Jack England表示，该组织里的50名成员与当地其他维持治安的人共同在大街上执行巡逻任务，并有90名成员加入了Enfield地区的治安队伍<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2024707/UK-riots-2011-Met-Polices-Tim-Godwin-warns-EDL-hijack-vigilante-patrols.html?ito=feeds-newsxml UK riots 2011: Met Police's Tim Godwin warns EDL could hijack vigilante patrols] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2024707/UK-riots-2011-Met-Polices-Tim-Godwin-warns-EDL-hijack-vigilante-patrols.html?ito=feeds-newsxml |date=20170205144228 }}, Daily Mail Online.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.channel4.com/news/police-clash-with-vigilantes-in-eltham |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-12 |archive-date=2011-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110901024342/http://www.channel4.com/news/police-clash-with-vigilantes-in-eltham |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 警察 ===
[[伦敦警察厅|伦敦警察厅]]声明是他们打击犯罪的行动诱发了骚乱，他们也会调查骚乱中发生的各种犯罪事件<ref name="guardian2"/><ref>{{cite web|title=London riots: Met Police launch major investigation|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14438109|publisher=BBC News|date=2011-08-07|accessdate=2011-08-10|archive-date=2011-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811192813/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14438109|dead-url=no}}</ref>。调查工作由警察厅的''John Sweeney''负责领导，还有来自{{tsl|en|Homicide and Serious Crime Command|凶殺及重案調查部}}的侦探们，来自{{tsl|en|Public Order Branch|公共秩序分部}}的调查专家，以及大量警员的支持<ref>{{cite|title=Statements following disorder in Tottenham|date=2011-08-07|publisher=Metropolitan Police Service}}</ref>。

[[大曼彻斯特|大曼彻斯特]]警察部门首长助理Garry Shewan，称这是“前所未有的”犯罪。10日他警告说“许许多多的人（指犯罪分子），我们已经掌握了你的照片，我们知道你的长相，我们有你们肆意妄为的视频”<ref>{{cite web |author=James Meikle and Sam Jones |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/aug/10/london-riots-spark-copycat-birmingham |title=UK riots: More than 1,000 arrests strain legal system to the limit | UK news |publisher=guardian.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2011-08-11 |archive-date=2013-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528055936/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/aug/10/london-riots-spark-copycat-birmingham |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

